    Calvin
    GOD IS REAL Im gonna try spare the sob story and stick to the facts this is gonna be long so take a smoke break 3 months ago my Roomates conspired against and had me arrested on a lie and thrown out like a dog while stealing my things in the process I was going through the process of the legal system to prove my innocence until last week I was removed from my post at my career job in security bc my guard license had been suspended bc of said charges pending I had thought I was past the part of being fired since I disclosed everything to the bosses and clients I had I was wrong. And i suddenly was removed without pay from my job last Monday morning while being told my career in security was likely over or at least for 6 month it wouldnt be up for review It was the perfect job the perfect gig to let me do mma I had worked hard for a year learning to love these clients and I took pride in the 3rd career Ive been able to start in my life and in a snap it was gone. Or was it? I was told I had two weeks to resolve the issue a shot in the dark a Hail Mary a snowballs chance in hell to get not just the court on bored but the dept of dps and the TOPs organization all to bend to my will and undo the suspension I did every legal step I could I got the case dissmissed I filed the appeal with dps I did all I could on my end and I prayed and let god handle it I thought it was over I was ready to have this last fight and move on I was broken all until about a hour ago when I got a email saying I had been reinstated and suddenly in a snap I had it all back And not only did I have it back I realized my faith and calling had been tested and I passed he made me see all the people who love and have invested into me Im not alone anymore Im more loved then I could ever imagine Ill never question if I iam built for this anymore or is this right for me anymore now I know my calling is true God is great he has always been there for me from when I was a suffering kid to the man I am today I apologize I ran it long but I dont apologize for giving praise to god bc man I truly didnt see the way out but I leaned not on my own understanding and here we are Jan 24th we write another chapter but the journey continues daily El Leprechaun out
    All reactions:
